Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:12.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried coming alone to our usual park.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:16.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a feeling I've never felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a child, frightened by the sound of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.67,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran back along the path home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:33.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky outside the window is too vast. Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, may this reach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:44.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Lord, if you ever grant wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:50.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grant my wish right now, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:56.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear your voice, I miss you! I want to see you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:01:00.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you already be looking toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:06.21,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just brush it off, saying the time has slipped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:08.54,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:14.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, and yet it's been too late since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:19.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give up, it can't be like the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:24.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just decide so simply there's no way, no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.23,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious plant-like creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that appeared at the White House have \Nshown their monstrous true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.58,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,Washington has issued an \Nemergency evacuation order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.37,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,And the well-being of the \NPresident and his staff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:51.98,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,who were in the White House before it \Nwas swallowed up is currently unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.00,Main Dialog I,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skrugg have reappeared, \Nbut I'm sure that Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sure that both \Nof them will do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can try again, but \Nit'll turn out the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop you... as many times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools can no longer stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:40.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this Earth is already well on \Nits way towards being annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.78,0:03:50.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:56.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will make you realize just how \Nmuch more powerful I am than that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've entered the airspace \Nof the bombing target!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Code entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Safeties disengaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really win with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's down there fighting \Nhis heart out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will accomplish our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to drop the storm gathering bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bombs away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of bombing the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:00.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're making the energy that we're \Ngoing to use to recharge Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bombs have a special compound in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:19.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This compound makes all the water vapor in \Nthe air gather together almost explosively!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty soon the entire sky will \Nbe covered with storm clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get those clouds to produce lightning, \Nand have it strike Heroman directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it works, he should be able to have plenty of \Nenergy to recover, just like the time he ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:49.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible to direct where \Nlighting strikes like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlook NOTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, lighting tries \Nto avoid traveling through air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:08.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it zig-zags as it falls \Nand strikes the tallest buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make use of that tendency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've installed special equipment on the MR-1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that can create an artificial \Nvacuum in the vicinity of Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, as it tries to avoid the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the lighting will strike toward the \Ninvisible vacuum that acts like a lightning rod,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Heroman's charging up will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:39.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why we've got to hurry and \Nget this thing near Heroman, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:42.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking you could oppose \Nme, as weak as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one that can stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make one false step, I'm done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:17.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are... the spheres!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spheres are heading toward Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spheres...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:57.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spheres are turning into a liquid, \Nand being absorbed by Kogorr!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hughes... What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:17.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our common wisdom is \Nuseless against the Skrugg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The spheres melted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those spheres, that humanity \Ncouldn't even scratch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where yer drivin', baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:43.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will devour this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I consume will \Nbecome my sustenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:49.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they are no exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Kogorr, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating his ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:17.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will become my food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move a bit farther away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a crucial moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the time to worry about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're shot down, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll keep filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just get some altitude, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:10:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's for the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We fell pretty far...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How are the preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you heading to the scene now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give orders more quickly observing \Nthe situation on the ground myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that from the cargo plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not use a helicopter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has complete \Ncontrol of the airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a great chance that we'd \Nbe shot down if we got too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, Mr. Denton's \Nplan seemed to be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:46.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about getting you involved \Nin something this dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're fighting in an \Neven more dangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just sit there doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from here, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:34.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to follow your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:42.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for my own fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your ally or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:53.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:03.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:07.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This weapon caused Heroman so much \Ntrouble, and now it's going to help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to say it, but we \Nreally owe Dr. Minami one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice and slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! It's about to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even more dangerous \Nto pull up too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So take it slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make up your damn mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...says them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This speed will do, according \Nto my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just the amazing \Npotential the MR-1 possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With it, we're going to save \NJoey and Heroman, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is the crystal on Kogorr's chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it after my body became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the weak point for all the Skrugg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:50.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can destroy that \Ncrystal, we can end it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:55.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I have to get up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You impudent little...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already predicted your every move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:15.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Augment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him, Joey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:50.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not where my weak point is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:32.40,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get to know you better,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:35.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to go at each other with our true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:41.83,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears and smile are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:46.26,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard it is, I won't be scared any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:49.32,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With both of us, we can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:54.76,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who taught me that I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I mutter the words "I was born to meet you"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:07.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,my unease disappears, and my heart burns stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:14.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.30,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Carve out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:23.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:28.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I live feeling the same heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you to the very last,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:32.68,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to protect the promise built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:40.08,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. We'll go on together with a sign only we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:45.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We are carving out this irreplaceable time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:52.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Heroman:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:54.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:23:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.91,0:24:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogorr continues to evolve \Nto his complete form,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and Heroman has fallen silent \Nafter being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While the countdown to Earth's destruction \Nbegins, Joey makes his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:12.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle heads toward its climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Heroman #26: Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.42,0:24:18.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroman!
